# Cursor

This file points to the canonical AI playbook for this repo.

Read AGENTS.md at the repo root before writing or editing code. It documents:

- the workspace layout and path aliases (`~/*`, `@kit/*`, `@provenance/*`)
- the Supabase client selection rules (server / admin / browser)
- the auth + roles + perspective model and `requireAdmin()` pattern
- the UI design system (parchment / ink / wine, Gotham, @kit/ui)
- the AI SDK 6 conventions (Vercel AI Gateway, `Output.object`, no edge runtime)
- the migrations + RLS + DATA-SAFE rule
- the Server Action / Route Handler / rate-limit / notifications conventions
- a cheat-sheet of recipes for the most common task types

The .mdc files in .cursor/rules/ remain authoritative for the rules they cover
(logging, data-safe migrations).
